<paragraph blockId="2.[136,1452,1747,2061]" pageId="2" pageNumber="167">
<emphasis box="[189,331,1856,1881]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="167">Description:</emphasis>
—Colonies on PDA reaching 
<quantity box="[660,782,1855,1881]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="3.9" metricValueMin="3.6" pageId="2" pageNumber="167" unit="mm" value="37.5" valueMax="39.0" valueMin="36.0">36−39 mm</quantity>
diam. after 2 wk at 25 °C, slimy appearance due to abundant sporulation on medium surface, orange to pale yellow in center, pinkish orange at margin. Colonies on MEA reaching 
<quantity box="[136,258,1927,1954]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.7" metricValueMax="3.9" metricValueMin="3.5" pageId="2" pageNumber="167" unit="mm" value="37.0" valueMax="39.0" valueMin="35.0">35−39 mm</quantity>
diam. after 2 wk at 25 °C, surface floccose, with white aerial mycelium, light cinnamon in center. Colonies on SNA reaching 
<quantity box="[334,456,1963,1989]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.7" metricValueMax="3.8" metricValueMin="3.6" pageId="2" pageNumber="167" unit="mm" value="37.0" valueMax="38.0" valueMin="36.0">36−38 mm</quantity>
diam. after 2 wk at 25 °C, aerial mycelium absent, sporulation on center medium surface, light yellow to white. Colonies on OA reaching 
<quantity box="[688,812,1999,2025]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.95" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.9" pageId="2" pageNumber="167" unit="mm" value="39.5" valueMax="40.0" valueMin="39.0">39−40 mm</quantity>
diam. after 2 wk at 25 °C, aerial mycelium absent with slimy appearance due to abundant sporulation on medium surface, light yellow.
</paragraph>
